    <p>In­door ver­ti­cal farm­ing com­pany &ever is set­ting up its global re­search and de­vel­op­ment cen­tre in Sin­ga­pore.</p>
    <p>The fa­cil­ity will be co-lo­cated with the Ger­man firm’s mega-farm in Changi, which is slated to be­gin op­er­a­tions in the fourth quar­ter of next year.</p>
    <p>The an­nounce­ment comes about a month af­ter the firm said it re­ceived a fund­ing award un­der the Sin­ga­pore Food Agency’s “30x30 Ex­press” grant to build its in­door ver­ti­cal farm. The R&D cen­tre will be set up with sup­port from the Eco­nomic De­vel­op­ment Board as well.</p>


